{"tid":2132060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府縮沙係咪因為意識到呢個世界唔係淨係得寫字樓同郊野公園？","createTime":"2020-07-30T08:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T08:23:05.000Z","uid":57036,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"931cccd49bd6395a141c63cb1f884ef2b89da1b7","tid":2132060,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"理想(張建宗)<br />\n1. 冇堂食，咪買番去自己寫字樓食<br />\n2. 冇寫字樓，我地都唔阻你去郊野公園，但要注意個人衛生<br />\n<br />\n現實<br />\n1. 好多勞力士(用勞力搵食既人士)係冇寫字樓，因為唔係渣筆搵食<br />\n2. 香港地石屎森林，撚有咁多郊野公園，得d屋邨遊樂場仔公園仔<br />\n3. 如果工作地點唔近公園仔，或者地盤唔比拎野番去食(就算比你都唔想撈塵食飯啦屌)，咪要踎街食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4718c42e44e809b911c2d617c1cac7edd5464784","tid":2132060,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"係因為弱智"},{"pid":"f78d758bc16c527e4e0ad8ab9e6f9f52d5e4c8ba","tid":2132060,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4718c42e44e809b911c2d617c1cac7edd5464784","tid":2132060,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"係因為弱智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}